          innovation, and environmental sustainability. Each track provides a focused platform for
          researchers, policymakers, and industry professionals to share their latest findings and
          collaborate on solutions.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-[#2C3E50]/80">
          Submissions are welcome across all tracks, and interdisciplinary approaches that span
          multiple areas are especially encouraged.
        </p>
      </div>
